    }
  ],
  "mediaType": "application/vnd.docker.distribution.manifest.list.v2+json",
  "schemaVersion": 2
}
```

The individual manifest digests can of course be used in a Docker reference to `skopeo copy` specific images, for example
`skopeo copy docker://alpine@sha256:e7d88de73db3d3fd9b2d63aa7f447a10fd0220b7cbf39803c803f2af9ba256b3   [destination]`
